{"_id":"MmYyNmE4YTcyOTdi","name":"Sahuagin Roster","content":"<section class=\"secret\"><p>GM Notes : </p><h2 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Sahuagin Roster, Level 1</h2><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 1</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 6 @Actor[MzIxNmM4MzI1NmVk]{sahuagin}, 2 @Actor[NTQ3OGQ1YmU4ZjFh]{sahuagin coral smashers}, 1 @Actor[MGE2ZTk2YjVmODA1]{sahuagin champion}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> These guards are alerted by intruders they become aware of. If one of them rings the gong three times, sahuagin in 2 and 12 rush to their aid.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 2</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 2 @Actor[MzIxNmM4MzI1NmVk]{sahuagin}<br /></li><li><b>Notes: </b>These guards go to 1 if they hear combat or if the gong is rung three times.</li></ul><hr /><h3>Area 12</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 5 @Actor[MzIxNmM4MzI1NmVk]{sahuagin}, 2 @Actor[NTQ3OGQ1YmU4ZjFh]{sahuagin coral smashers}, 2 @Actor[ZGU3MTZlYTcwYWFk]{sahuagin priestesses}</li><li><b>Notes: </b>These sahuagin go to 1 if the gong is rung three times or if they are alerted by a guard from 2.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 13</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> @Actor[M2UyNWYzOTZkZTRl]{Elmo the slave}</li><li><b>Notes: </b>Elmo is near death and cannot be moved.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 19</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 2 @Actor[MzIxNmM4MzI1NmVk]{sahuagin}, 4 @Actor[NTQ3OGQ1YmU4ZjFh]{sahuagin coral smashers}, 1 @Actor[MGE2ZTk2YjVmODA1]{sahuagin champion}, 1 @Actor[ZGU3MTZlYTcwYWFk]{sahuagin priestess}, 10 slaves</li><li><b>Notes: </b>These sahuagin go to 12 if they hear sounds of combat from that area. The slaves remain here.</li></ul><hr /><h2 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Sahuagin Roster, Level 2</h2><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 23</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 2 @Actor[MGE2ZTk2YjVmODA1]{sahuagin champions}, 2 @Actor[ZGU3MTZlYTcwYWFk]{sahuagin priestesses}</li><li><b>Notes: </b>These sahuagin remain here until encountered.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 24</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 25 @Actor[MzIxNmM4MzI1NmVk]{sahuagin}, 5 @Actor[NTQ3OGQ1YmU4ZjFh]{sahuagin coral smashers}, 5 @Actor[MGE2ZTk2YjVmODA1]{sahuagin champions}</li><li><b>Notes: </b>Guard patrols are drawn from this area until all the occupants are defeated.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 25</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 3 @Actor[M2Y4ZmZmN2RhMmVj]{sahuagin hatchling swarms}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> If the swarms emerge, 5 sahuagin and 1 coral smasher come here from 24.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 26</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 2 @Actor[ZGU3MTZlYTcwYWFk]{sahuagin priestesses}, 2 @Actor[M2Y4ZmZmN2RhMmVj]{sahuagin hatchling swarms} </li><li><b>Notes:</b> The swarms emerge if the priestesses are alerted. The priestesses try to flee to 24; if one does so, it returns with 5 sahuagin and 1 coral smasher.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 27</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 1 @Actor[MGE2ZTk2YjVmODA1]{sahuagin champion}, 12 @Actor[MzIxNmM4MzI1NmVk]{sahuagin}, 12 @Actor[NTQ3OGQ1YmU4ZjFh]{sahuagin coral smashers}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> These sahuagin remain here until encountered.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 28</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 1 @Actor[ODE3YWNiYTg5NjI5]{sahuagin wave shaper}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> The wave shaper goes to 27 if alerted by sounds of combat there, arriving on the third round.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 29</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 1 @Actor[MGE2ZTk2YjVmODA1]{sahuagin champion}, 10 @Actor[MzIxNmM4MzI1NmVk]{sahuagin}, 6 @Actor[NTQ3OGQ1YmU4ZjFh]{sahuagin coral smashers}, 4 @Actor[NDQ4ZTI0MmYyMWJk]{sahuagin deep divers}, 4 @Actor[NGVkNTY2ZGVkZTQ1]{shell sharks}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> These sahuagin remain here until encountered.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 30</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 1 @Actor[MGE2ZTk2YjVmODA1]{sahuagin champion}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> The champion goes to 29 if alerted by sounds of combat there.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 34</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 1 @Actor[ZGU3MTZlYTcwYWFk]{sahuagin priestess}, 4 @Actor[NGVkNTY2ZGVkZTQ1]{shell sharks}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> These creatures remain here until encountered.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 37</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> @Actor[NjIzM2ZiMmM4OTkx]{Maw of Sekolah}, 3 @Actor[ZGU3MTZlYTcwYWFk]{sahuagin priestesses}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> These creatures remain here until encountered.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quo