tor[MzIxNmM4MzI1NmVk]{sahuagin}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> These sahuagin remain here until encountered.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 55</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 2 @Actor[MGE2ZTk2YjVmODA1]{sahuagin champions}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> These sahuagin go to 54 if alerted by sounds of combat there.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 56</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 2 @Actor[ODE3YWNiYTg5NjI5]{sahuagin wave shapers}, 6 @Actor[MzIxNmM4MzI1NmVk]{sahuagin}, 2 @Actor[NGVkNTY2ZGVkZTQ1]{shell sharks}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> These creatures remain here until encountered.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 57</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 1 @Actor[ODE3YWNiYTg5NjI5]{sahuagin wave shaper}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> The wave shaper goes to 56 if alerted by sounds of combat there.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 58</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 2 @Actor[MGE2ZTk2YjVmODA1]{sahuagin champions}, 6 @Actor[MzIxNmM4MzI1NmVk]{sahuagin}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> These sahuagin go to 54 if alerted by sounds there, arriving in 3 rounds.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 59</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 1 @Actor[MGE2ZTk2YjVmODA1]{sahuagin champion}, 1 @Actor[MzIxNmM4MzI1NmVk]{sahuagin}</li><li><b>Notes:</b> These sahuagin remain here until encountered.</li></ul><hr /><h3 style=\"font-family:&quot;helvetica neue&quot; , &quot;helvetica&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif\">Area 60</h3><ul><li><b>Occupants at Start:</b> 45 @Actor[MzIxNmM4MzI1NmVk]{sahuagin}, 10 @Actor[NTQ3OGQ1YmU4ZjFh]{sa