{"_id":"NDE5ODk3YjJiOWI5","name":"Pressure Capsule","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"ODU3ZmEyODkxOTk5","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":24,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":240000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h4>Pressure Capsule</h4><p><i>Wondrous item, common</i></p><p>This small capsule is made of beeswax blended with sand and a variety of enchanted water plants. A creature who consumes a<i> pressure capsule</i> ignores the effects of swimming at depths greater than 100 feet.</p>","img":""}
