{"_id":"Y2U1NTI4ZTAyYjlm","name":"Entertainer (Background)","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"NDY5MzUzOTM2NTBh","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":4,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":40000,"entryTime":0,"content":"\n<section class=\"secret\"><p>GM Notes : </p><h2>Entertainer</h2><p>Bards and performers are always in demand in Saltmarsh. You can use your By Popular Demand feature to find work at the Wicker Goat or the Snapping Line. The Wicker Goat is popular with the town guard and the dwarves who work the mine outside town, while The Snapping Line is frequented by fishers, sailors, and laborers who work the docks. Choose one of those taverns as your preferred venue. The staff, owner, and regulars there treat you as a friend.<br><br></p></section>","img":""}
