{"_id":"ZmMxOGViNmYwMDM5","name":"Potion of Water Breathing","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"NmZiOTM2OTUxNmEy","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":5,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":50000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h4 style=\"font-family: &#34;helvetica neue&#34; , &#34;helvetica&#34; , &#34;arial&#34; , sans-serif\">Potion of Water Breathing</h4><p><i>Potion, uncommon</i><br></p><p>You can breathe underwater for 1 hour after drinking this potion. Its cloudy green fluid smells of the sea and has a jellyfish-like bubble floating in it.</p>","img":""}
